name: Sheep's Head
description:
Sub-title: “Lovecraftian Floral Horror 002”

Second in My ongoing series of cosmic horror floral nightmares. Tropical flowers are mutated and distorted by some nameless, alien god to form a disturbing face reminiscent of a sheep's head.

Two artificial intelligence systems (VQGAN+CLIP) created this work. No input image was used.

2752x2752 pixel PNG

Minted December 11th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or vqgan.tormential.tez
